      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经配置好了init参数，debug级别日志，theme用base。现在branch_1上有commit \"x\"，三个分支也已经创建好了。接下来怎么安排各分支的提交？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "init",
        "logLevel",
        "theme",
        "commit x"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "切换到branch_2，先做两个commit，标记为\"a\"和\"b\"。然后切回branch_1做一个commit \"y\"。接着去branch_3做\"e\"和\"f\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "branch_2",
        "commit a",
        "commit b",
        "commit y",
